Add Organizational Unit to RNC search

DEPENDE DA #2985 (closed) #2972 (closed)

IMPROVEMENT FOR US-23

Definition of Ready

  • Atualizar critérios de aceitação.
  • Atualizar telas desenhadas pelo design, considerando fluxo atual e telas mobile.
  • Textos traduzidos.
  • Atualizar cenários de testes criados.

História de usuário:

  • US-23

Critérios de aceitação:

Simplifield Search It must filter and return results , of any of the below filters (in the same way as today  in risk Analysis on Risk module , in the leacy system):

  • Author
  • Description
  • Process
  • Organizational Unit
  • Status
  • Root Cause
  • notes
  • Only on time action
  • Only Delayed Actions

Design:

https://www.figma.com/file/QE5y1CdFDU6qug7ykbbqyy/2974-Add-Organizational-Unit-to-RNC-search?node-id=7%3A174

Traduções:

Organizational unit
Unidad organizacional
组织单元

Cenários de teste:

Adiocionado cenário 25

Scenario 25

GIVEN I am on the search screen using the advanced search filter
AND I have a nonconformity registered with “NC US-23 scenario 25” description
AND “NC_US-23” as the nonconformity Organizational unit
WHEN I search for “NC_US-23” in the nonconformity Organizational unit
THEN the nonconformity “NC US-23 scenario 25” should be found
